Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.15,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the sports festival is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:22.90,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,I actually have time \Nto admire the cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:24.21,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The seasons have changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:26.93,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and springtime has come again \Nto Hino-Minami High,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.88,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,where Koshitan and the others go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:33.06,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when I said this series wasn't \Nstuck in the Sazae-san space-time dimension?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:34.38,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:37.64,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\bord1\fnArial Black\c&H231C12&\3c&H2C50C3&\pos(410.286,68.857)}Deer Club\N{\fs10}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:37.64,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Might be about time to enjoy some cherry-\Nblossom viewing in front of the clubhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:40.08,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:51.00,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Shikanoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:52.55,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Koshitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:55.21,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying? Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:58.78,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you hungry? \NWe have plenty of deer crackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:58.78,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(564,1)\fs16\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H402529&\3c&H97685F&\pos(554.857,121.428)}Deer Crackers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:04.54,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even sad, but I just can't \Nstop crying for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:08.63,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.34,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because it's spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:14.09,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Shikanoko... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:17.97,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,You probably have allergies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:56.03,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\bord1.5\fnArial Black\c&HFB7BFB&\3c&H8DFBCF&\pos(318.5,118.5)}Blame It on the Spring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.78,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, nah, nah, nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.63,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,What are you even talking about, Koshitan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:01.78,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Did you happen to forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.91,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I am a deer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.66,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I am Nokotan the deer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:08.50,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Allergies only affect you humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.54,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they'd affect a deer like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:15.79,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is that symptom?! \NIs that actually an allergy symptom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:19.17,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,It itches! Everything itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:42.15,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stop crying. But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.42,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you. You have allergies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.18,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Objection! It's absolutely not allergies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:50.10,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Allergies could never bring a wild deer down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:52.54,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So what {\i1}do{\i0} you think is causing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.25,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:58.48,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so damn stubborn! \NThose aren't cold symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:02.68,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Also, what's with people who get allergies \Nhating to ever admit they have allergies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.84,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Just Allergy Things, number one:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.16,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,When people with allergies \Nabsolutely deny having them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:09.79,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what that's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.68,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.04,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:16.59,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,But lucky me! I can't believe I've \Nhappened upon this bizarre situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:19.31,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this opening to disband the Deer Clubâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:25.66,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,It itches! It itches! It itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:39.96,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:43.07,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not have allergies, then, Koshitan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.85,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:49.68,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't once suffered from allergies in my \Nseventeen years on Earth, and I never will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.93,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Just Allergy Things, number two:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:55.59,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,People who are oddly confident \Nthat they will never have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:58.21,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Koshitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.83,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,You're just some dumb human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.46,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Pfft, say whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.83,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,You're just some former delinquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:05.61,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,And you like girly things, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.49,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,What's that got to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:10.69,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on with some human \Nwho doesn't understand this pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:13.08,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,We're disbanding the Deer Club as of today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:14.31,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Over something this trivial?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.12,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Their paths have diverged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.78,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,The Deer Club is disbanding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:20.54,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Finally my ambition is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:26.86,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.88,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Just Allergy Things, number three:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:32.64,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,When people lose out on golden opportunities \Nbecause they can't think straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.41,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I can't believe it's gotten this bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:38.32,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,After being villainized as an enemy \Nof humanity since time immemorial,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.72,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,cedar pollen is finally taking its revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.30,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have allergies, too, Kinu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.40,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,She does not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.40,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs20\fnTimes New Roman\c&H050011&\3c&H110F80&\pos(492,225.429)}Student Council
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.25,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,Kinu, do you have any tissues?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.83,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. I only have this handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.24,Default,Tanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Want to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.80,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Vice President,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:57.88,Default,Tsubame,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we go back to the student \Ncouncil office so you can blow your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.51,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,At least wash all that floof off of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.04,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get you a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.80,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that feels so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:16.43,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,But it still feels itchy deep in my antlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.61,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish washing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.49,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I feel alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.44,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell am I witnessing \Nright now? Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.33,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.31,Default,Floof,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.75,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,We have pollination!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:41.25,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,It definitely feels like springtime is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.59,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(173,1)\fs25\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H32282D&\3c&H3B77BB&\pos(313.714,172.286)}Deer Club\N{\fs15}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.89,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it! It still itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.87,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Just Allergy Things, number four:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.22,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Allergy-inspired rage that has no outlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.66,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, they make \Nglasses for people with allergies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.94,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,They're designed to keep \Npollen out of the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:06:58.99,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:03.36,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah! I borrowed some goggles \Nfrom the swim team!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:04.57,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:07.49,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I don't itch anymore! Now I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.65,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't got nothin' on me, allergies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:18.40,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,My antlers are itching again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.87,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.75,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Did... Did your antlers just sneeze?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.00,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have some tissues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.48,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you feel a sneeze coming on, \Nblow your antlers with those.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:29.03,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I want fancy tissues like Antler Celeb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.60,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Quit being picky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.26,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.51,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,My nose is stuffed up, \Nso my voice is all nasally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:38.77,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,You sound super weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:44.64,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why do these horrible things \Njust keep happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:47.90,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to act like a tragic \Nheroine with snot coming out of your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.82,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Living in a world like this \Nis too much! I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.53,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H131216&\3c&H1140A4&\pos(349.142,132.858)}Deer Club\N{\fs10}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.53,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.59,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.04,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.53,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fsp6\bord4\fnArial Black\c&H070E72&\3c&H399D4E&\frz1.756\fax-0.05\pos(330.643,174.643)}Hi{\c&H266CE9&\3c&HAAB8F0&}no {\c&H4BC7D8&\3c&H399D4E&}Z{\c&HA67F2B&\3c&HAAB8F0&}o{\c&H6C0F32&\3c&H399D4E&}o
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.60,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.89,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:10.85,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... Are you here to cheer me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.28,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Even you, Tsunoda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.68,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,And they're here again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:18.44,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks... I won't let this get me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:21.06,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I just had a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.48,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Let's burn down the cedar trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.44,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not say something so ominous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:28.36,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, burning down the \Ncedar trees in the neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.51,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,isn't gonna fix your allergiesâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:31.19,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Koshitan, did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:35.95,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,My antlers have a dynamite version, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:43.99,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,And I've shed a lot of antlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.35,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:49.06,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,With these, I'm going to blow up \Nevery last cedar grove in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:52.01,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not store explosives \Nin the clubhouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:55.91,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I will return it all to nothing, so that \Na new world can rise from the ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.26,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the final boss spiel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.76,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,I want in on that plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.14,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Nekoyamada-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.41,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Comrade Shikayamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.64,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,It's Nekoyamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:09.97,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,What's one thing our world \Nwould be better off without?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:12.76,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you... Cedars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:13.90,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.34,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Say no to pollen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:16.56,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,No to pollen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.79,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Say no to pollen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.09,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,No to pollen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.27,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Say no to pollen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.74,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,No to pollen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:27.53,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hold on a sec. There's probably \Nsomething I should mention first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.79,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Something you should mention?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.80,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H0607F8&\3c&HFFF5DD&}Hino Veterinary Hospital {\alpha&HFF&\t(1071,2156,\alpha&H00&)}for Doggies and Kitties
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.80,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't like hospitals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.41,Default,Vet,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Just stay still for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:42.83,Default,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here, too?! I'm not a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.94,Default,Vet,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Just stay still for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:48.02,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hate me. This is part \Nof my job as your owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.27,Default,Floof,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.65,Default,Receptionist,0000,0000,0000,,Koshi-san, you can head \Ninto the exam room next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.53,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:58.78,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Just Allergy Things, number five:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:03.93,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,When someone who swears they'll never \Nsuffer from allergies finally gets them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:08.04,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs24\pos(22.215,105.786)}Izu Peninsula\NHachijo-jima
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.54,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs24\pos(22.786,112.643)}Hachijo-jima\NReeves's muntjacs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.55,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H1B1537&\3c&H2457BC&\pos(409.714,68.286)}Deer Club\N{\fs10}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:17.42,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Shikanoko hasn't been coming \Nto the Deer Club lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:20.43,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. Where's she slacking off at?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:26.93,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fnTimes New Roman\fs22\c&H250A86&\3c&H58B4DE&\bord2\pos(361.428,93.858)}D{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}e{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r {\3c&H58B4DE&}C{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r{\3c&H58B4DE&}a{\3c&HF9FBFF&}c{\3c&H58B4DE&}k{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}r{\3c&HF9FBFF&}s
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:23.59,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,So it's been a week since she \Nwas last at the clubhouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:25.81,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,That's actually pretty long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:31.03,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do Deer Club activities \Nwithout our deer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.53,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,What could she possibly be up to, and where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:37.52,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,She's been coming to school, so it's just her \Nafter-school whereabouts that are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:41.81,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Did she quit the Deer Club \Nand join some other club?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:46.95,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... This castle I've made for myself, \Nnot to mention the Deer Club, is in peril!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:49.84,Flashback,Ukai,0000,0000,0000,,A club with no deer cannot stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:53.71,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just sit here! We're going \Nto look for Shikanoko, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.59,Default,Anko and Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:57.71,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.35,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I ended up having \Nto look for her all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.47,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs9\c&H313340&\3c&HFAFBFF&\bord2\fay-0.12\move(507.428,102.572,485.714,126.572,26,1986)}Flower Arrangement Club
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.47,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\c&H1F1F1F&\3c&HF8F8F8&\fay-0.28\pos(321.715,118.571)}Flower Arrangement Club
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:07.47,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,The Flower Arrangement Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:10.73,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,It seems oddly lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:15.71,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem. We have a special \Nlecturer visiting us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:17.19,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nokotan-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:20.36,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.74,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Nokotan-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.87,Default,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,You're so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.45,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is Shikanoko doing \Nin the Flower Arrangement Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.10,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,And what did she mean by special lecturer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:31.92,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's have our lecturer \Nperform a flower arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.88,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:38.13,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? Like she'd know anything \Nabout flower arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:39.85,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.70,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,What's this sudden atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:47.64,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Could she have some knack for it \Nthat I didn't know about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.39,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Shikanoko Style Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.27,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:08.47,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use your damn head for a flower bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.29,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,There's a thing called being too free!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.14,Default,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,That's so impressive, Nokotan-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.63,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than flowers, she arranged her antlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.29,Default,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:19.17,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,So you agree. \NIt's not a flower arrangement at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.11,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've never seen such technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:53.12,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0} technique?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:55.81,Default,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Her flower-less arrangement \Nwas already impressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.91,Default,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,but with her bold new crumb-\Nscattering idea on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:01.66,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,This could change the history \Nof flower arrangement forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.63,Default,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,It's a revolution in the \Nflower-arrangement world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:08.01,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Again, this isn't even \Nflower arrangement anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:11.82,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I knew my eye for talent didn't fail me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:20.02,Flashback,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,May a thousand antlers bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:27.53,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't forgotten how your artwork \Nthat day resonated with my very soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:32.91,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Nokotan-sensei, would you be so kind \Nas to tell us the title of this piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.05,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,"Tsuno to Shika."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:38.92,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds very similar to a Yonezu Kenshi \Nsong title from a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.54,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,It's... It's just so deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:45.63,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,How?! It's not deep! \NIt's actually pretty damn shallow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:49.33,Default,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,So this uses the deer crackers \Nto represent the parched earth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:53.58,Default,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,and expresses the bond that was born \Nfrom deer and humans living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:54.47,Default,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,It's genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:57.77,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing, Nokotan-sensei. I'm in awe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.98,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i0}seriously{\i1} overthinking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:06.28,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's have Nokotan-sensei \Nobserve all of your works.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.13,Default,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Please look at mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.18,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,No, mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.36,Default,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,Mine first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:13.77,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. I'll look at all of yours \Nin order, one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.68,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, an idol handshake event?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:21.75,Default,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I tried to express the beauty \Nof springtime with this piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:27.82,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite lovely. But I also \Nfeel like it lacks impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:31.50,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, considering what you all just saw, \Neverything's gonna lack impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.38,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.31,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.54,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, er, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.48,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,It needs better nutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.40,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Are you giving advice to some college freshman \Nthat just started living on their own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:44.84,Default,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.65,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly made sense there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.93,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,All you need is a bit of wildness, \Ncuteness, umami, and some antlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:51.64,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,And a pinch of salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:55.16,Default,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! How did I not notice it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:59.08,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Is that necessary? No, really. Is any of \Nthat necessary for flower arrangement?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:02.03,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you get once \Nyou add all those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.08,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,So graphic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.61,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd the "beauty of spring" aspect go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:10.09,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Are we in a jungle?! Also, don't \Njust add onto someone else's piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:11.24,Default,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,It's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.09,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as she's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.94,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,And for the final touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:24.11,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, why a guitar?! And do you have an \Nextra-dimensional pocket in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:48.75,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... What even is this performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:50.87,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even a proper song.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:55.48,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh god, it's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:58.60,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I've seen these things on TV before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.23,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,The flowers... are alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.31,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,With the sound of music?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.11,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:09.03,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I was right about you, \NNokotan-sensei! My eyes never lieâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:15.87,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,See? This is what you get for \Nsaying something so clichÃ©d!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:19.55,Default,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that with birth \Nalso comes death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.10,Default,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,It's the circle of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:25.88,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,The god of the flower arrangement worldâ€”\Nno, of the new world has been born!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.12,Default,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shoo-in for the Nobel Prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:31.63,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, quit flower arrangement right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:37.76,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dearie me. It's about \Ntime to leave school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:41.85,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Senseiâ€”no, O God! \NPlease continue tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.82,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be coming tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.27,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Then the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.34,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be coming to the Flower \NArrangement Club anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:52.03,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,No! But you have so much talent! So why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.28,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,The novelty's worn off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.90,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:57.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to the new world you've shown us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.19,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:00.84,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,The Flower Arrangement Club's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.29,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\bord2\pos(321.714,124.286)}The Next Day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.29,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H3D2525&\3c&H2559AB&\pos(409.714,58.571)}Deer Club\N{\fs10}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.80,Default,Nokotan,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats the Deer Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.92,Default,Koshitan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.30,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs24\pos(18.79,160)}\NA very cute\NReeves's muntjac\Nfrom Hachijo-jima
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:31.32,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect day for planting some rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.70,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:44.33,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Anko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:46.21,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:54.96,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&H250A86&\3c&H58B4DE&\bord2\pos(355.714,70.429)}D{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}e{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r {\3c&H58B4DE&}C{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r{\3c&H58B4DE&}a{\3c&HF9FBFF&}c{\3c&H58B4DE&}k{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}r{\3c&HF9FBFF&}s
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.03,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,But Bashame hasn't said anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.13,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Did I guess wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.44,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:57.71,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Come plant some rice with me, Anko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:18:00.11,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don't want to get dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:03.97,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,But Bashame cultivated the land, \Nall to plant Bashame's rice paddy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:06.25,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame spent seven episodes on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.57,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,It's a product of Bashame's \Nblood, sweat, and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.61,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Seven episodes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:14.52,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Bashame promises you \Na completely new experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:16.31,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:17.92,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,You just won't take the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.31,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:22.72,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you didn't get permission from the \Nschool for your rice paddy, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:24.58,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.43,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This could very well be a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:34.51,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Who were you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.13,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Tsu... Tsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.12,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Tsudayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:38.02,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Tsucchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:40.39,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, exactly. Tsucchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:43.26,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Tsucchi! Let's plant some rice together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:45.27,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.27,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:59.80,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now that you've agreed, \Nit's time to plant some rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.53,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.38,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Ricey rice, ricey rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:07.79,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H2A1E16&\3c&H2249AA&\pos(490.286,173.429)}Deer Club\N{\fs15}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:09.79,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Hino City specialty Bashame Rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:13.67,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Come one, come all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:17.66,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a moment, come have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:22.30,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Some delicious, delicious, Bashame Rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:33.37,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, not bad, Tsudayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:40.03,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's time for Bashame \Nto reveal her true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.90,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, now we have to start all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:59.03,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't enough to keep Bashame down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:04.23,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, so you're still rarin' to go, Tsudayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:06.80,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's do this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:17.32,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H2A1E16&\3c&H407FC9&\pos(490.286,173.429)}Deer Club\N{\fs15}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:20.57,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two. Are you \Ndone planting your rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:23.03,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Anko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:25.32,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,We just finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:29.28,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, planting rice really is dirty work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.61,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I didn't help out after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.21,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Rice balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:36.79,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.80,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:47.65,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Your rice balls can easily \Nget three stars, Anko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:50.56,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm honored. Are you \Nenjoying your meal, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.60,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,You're really nice, Anko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:59.73,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. I'm just used \Nto making packed lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:03.36,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you make the\Npacked lunches, Anko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:06.54,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because my sister sucks at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:18.21,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,The rice planting's all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:23.92,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:36.42,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're growing rice and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:39.17,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you pickle some plums?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.53,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Anko-chan, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.53,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.90,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess we know what you're doing next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:50.03,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:59.77,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H32282D&\3c&H2A55AB&\move(324.571,98,324.571,324.286,28,9705)}Deer Club\N{\fs10}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.51,0:21:55.64,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a rice ball party in the fall with \Nsome Bashame Rice and Bashame Pickled Plums!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.64,0:21:56.74,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.74,0:22:00.95,Default,Bashame,0000,0000,0000,,We should get some chickens \Nso we can eat some egg over rice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:03.59,Default,Anko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Some yakitori would be good, too.

